Class SensorType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xpmnt.selfdriver.domain.SensorType

  • public class SensorType
extends java.lang.Object
    SensorType is a flyweight class similar to an enum but with structural complexities making it impossible to represent as a Java Enum. (Perhaps a refactoring is in order to separate out the anomalous speed limit type. As a flyweight with private constructors, it allows reference equality checks.
